{{Quote|Ten years ago, when Star Wars premiered, I never dreamed that I would be writing a letter to members of a Lucasfilm Fan Club. What a decade this has been.|[[George Lucas]]|<ref name="Most Memorable">{{SW|url=news/star-wars-insider-200-cover-retrospective|text=As ''Star Wars Insider'' Hits 200, a Look Back at Some of the Legendary Magazine's Most Memorable Issues}}</ref>}}
'''''The Lucasfilm Fan Club Magazine'' 1''' is the premiere issue of [[Star Wars Insider|''The Lucasfilm Fan Club Magazine'']], later rebranded as the ''Star Wars Insider''. Issue 1 was published in Fall [[1987]].

==Contents==
===Features===
*"A Letter from George Lucas" by [[George Lucas]] and "Welcome Back!!" {{C|by [[Hyperspace: The Official Star Wars Fan Club|The Lucasfilm Fan Club]]}}
*"[[Anthony Daniels: Remembering That Galaxy Far, Far Away]]" {{C|by [[Dan Madsen]] and John S. Davis}}
*"''Willow'': Forget All You Know, Or Think You Know"
*"[[Star Wars 10th Anniversary Convention!!|''Star Wars'' 10th Anniversary Convention!!]]"
*"[[Star Wars: Ten Year Tribute|''Star Wars'': Ten Year Tribute]]"
*"''Tucker''"

===Departments===
*"[[Looking At Lucasfilm]]" {{C|by [[Robert Allan]]}}
*"[[Inside ILM]]: The Art of Special Effects" {{C|by [[John S. Davis]]}}
*"[[Collections]]" {{C|by [[Adam Schultz]]}}

